Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I'm a physician. I've been a psychiatrist for 35 years, worked in the field\Nof psychoanalysis, worked in the field of nutrition, and especially nutrition and its relationship to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,brain chemistry. For the last 10 years, I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness\Nitself, and especially its relationship to that which the world calls spiritual. In today's talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be looking at the subject of health, one which everyone is interested in,\Nthe subject of health which occupies the minds of a large part of our population. And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as a physician, and as a psychiatrist, and as a spiritual researcher, I've been very interested\Nin the field of health and self-healing. So we'll be talking again about the relationship between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,body, mind, and spirit, because we know from our previous talks,\Nthat body has no way of experiencing itself, that body is experienced in mind only.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in mind that you experience the body. We know that the body expresses that which is held\Nin mind. We know that mind itself cannot really experience itself. It has to be experienced from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,an even greater energy field, which we call consciousness. So we go from dense form,\Never expanding into ever increasing formlessness. And so we end up with the experiencing of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,experience itself, or that field called awareness, which is beyond consciousness itself.\NSo we're looking today at that relationship between body, mind, and spirit, very important
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're considering the whole subject of health. We'll be looking at consciousness itself,\Nbecause all experience is going on within consciousness itself. And because the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the energy fields here, we've discovered that healing comes out of attitudes\Nand belief systems and that which is held in mind. And therefore, health is also coming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,out of expressions of levels of consciousness. And to understand this and make it more understandable,\Nmore comprehensible, especially to people who are very logical in the orientation, which
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was of course, being a skeptical scientist, what we've done is prepared here an integrated\Nmap of consciousness based on a mathematical relationship between the energy fields. And
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field that we've done, and myself and my coworker, Glorian Ross, over the last\Nfew years, in which we've calibrated the energy fields of literally tens of thousands of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitudes, feelings, etc.\NAnd so we've come up with this mathematical model in which the relative power of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,fields is calibrated so that you see that apathy, which is calibrated at 50, has only\Nhalf the power of fear, which is calibrated at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear on the other hand has only half the power or the energy of courage, which is calibrated\Nat 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do these energy fields have different relative power to each other, but we see that\Nthe energy fields go in a certain direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that all the energy fields under courage are directed in a negative, anti-life, that\Nwhich is oriented towards destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy fields below courage then tend to be anti-life in their effect.\NAt the level of courage we see that the needle swings to the midline, and we see that as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we go beyond the energy field of 200, up to neutral willingness, acceptance and love,\Nthere isn't much that is going on behind that Iraq and umas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.\NSewed to the left, I'll have a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now let's see how this would work .I'll have Buch constructed to 100, okay, this is\Nthat these energy fuels now go to the right, indicating that they nurture and support life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are energy-giving, life-giving, increasing aliveness.\NSo as we go up the scale, we go into energy fuels of increasing aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that which supports life and the truth.\NAnd as we get to the bottom of the field, we get to that which does not support life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which is anti-life, and which does not represent the truth.\NYou'll notice that death is calibrated at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we start with death at zero and calibrate these fields,\Nwe will find that at about the level of 600, we leave the field of duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We leave the field of illusion.\NWe leave the identification with the small self, with that which is the ego, in common parlance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we move on into fields of enlightenment, so that the great enlightened beings,\Nthe great spiritual masters, the avatars,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy fuels calibrate and begin up in the 700s and go on up into infinity.\NSo the truth really begins then, where this needle swings to neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving falsehood, going into truth,\Nand the energy fuels now go to the right, indicating that which is supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Supportive of life, supportive of aliveness.\NAnd so in our talk today, where we're talking about health, we're talking about aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're talking about truth.\NWe're talking about truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about truth.\NWe're talking about truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're talking about is the expression of an energy field.\NThe expression of an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said that the body expresses that which the mind holds.\NWe're only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the greater the negativity that is being held in mind,\Nthe greater the negative energy field effect on the body's physical health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The greater the positive energy being held in mind and consciousness,\Nthe more powerfully positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more positive will be the energy field of life.\NSo this gives us a tool now, a way of approaching things to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,does this support life or does it not support life?\NWe can substitute the word health, because health is nothing but the expression of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These things up here, we will find, are supporting health.\NAnd these things down here are creating illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the bottom of the box, we have energy fuels that support illness.\NAnd at the top of the box, we have energy fuels that support illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the bottom of the box, we have energy fuels that support health.\NAnd at the top of the box, we have energy fuels that support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of these energy fields reflects themselves in an emotion.\NSo that which is anti-life, as you would expect, has negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotions of self-hatred, hopelessness, despair, regret, depression, worry, anxiety,\Ncravingness, resentment, hatred, arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These negative emotions then accompany ill health.\NWe see the process going on in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the process going on in consciousness, coming out of the body,\NWe see the process going on in consciousness, coming out of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of these emotional states destruction loss of energy loss of spirit deflation entrapment\Nover expansion over inflation loss of power we see the kind of a world that a person experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,out of these negative mental states a world of sin and suffering hopelessness sadness frightening\Nfrustrating competitive a world of status we see the negative conceptualizations of god that come
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,out of a lower energy field god is the ultimate enemy of man the one who hates them hates him\Nthe destroyer the one who throws you into hell forever or the god who ignores you the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,unlovingness the god who's dead the god is punitive the god is retaliatory or the atheistic\Nor the bigot position so we have an energy field we have its negative direction we can see the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,weakness of the power we can see the negative emotion the destructive\Nand process going on in consciousness the negative view of the world and the negative
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,view of god all correlate with ill health all correlate with ill health is that accidental\Nis it causal so we'll be looking at that today we'll be looking at health as the expression of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,unopposed aliveness resulting from the removal of its obstacles from the removal of all that is\Nnegative and we'll see that health results from transcending limitation and feelings of separation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have the power of refusal we can refuse things that are negative in our life\Nif our mind can get programmed in a negative direction we can choose to program it in a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,positive direction we'll be looking at health as an expression of self-love\Njust how does one learn learn to love oneself we'll build an understanding of the subject then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:09:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,based on um our knowledge of these energy fields and their applications in everyday life and how to\Napply them to our daily lives this includes our way of thinking how do we live our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we take our time to think we get excited about ourselves and do things that we like and we\Nsee that there's a lot of life that we can do and we can do it we've all got healthy states
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of body health so even if we do more often we can have better health and also more energy\Nthe same way we can have better physical health we can have better health and when we have more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,health we can have better mental health like we can have better cognitive health and so on and so on\Ncatch out of the corner of your eye and not central to your experience at all that means
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go of identifying oneself as this physicalness and so on the scale of consciousness\Nhere as we get towards the bottom of the box we have an increasing identification of ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as being the body and as we move higher in our consciousness this lessons and lessons until we\Nfinally transcend that identification with the body and in move into the realization of spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the relationship between body mind and spirit then is what we'll be looking at today and how\Nto achieve optimal health we have to look at the relationship between mind and body because that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is of great importance in the field of health and one that is not really clearly understood\Nperhaps utilizing our map of consciousness we can make it clearer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is a\Ncertain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,principle and it's demonstrated clinically and we'll get to clinical examples\Nthat we're only subject to what we hold in mind now this is a principle of healing and a principle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of health the health and healing being two different sides of a coin illness being one side\Nof the coin health the other the opposite sides of the coin of the same understanding the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding that heals brings about health that we're subject to what we're holding in mind good\Nclinical
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,example of this as we said in a talk that we gave on healing illness is that of multiple\Npersonalities and another example is of hypnosis under hypnosis we can give a suggestion to a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,patient that you are allergic to the roses on the desk and when you wake up you will get hives\Nand a rash and start sneezing and then we create amnesia for that suggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when the person wakes up from the hypnotic trance all of a sudden they start to wheeze\Nthey get hives and develop a rash so the body you see is responding to what the mind believes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and so with hypnosis we can induce the symptoms and i would imagine probably almost any illness\Nby convincing the patient under hypnosis that our program that we have just programmed him with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually true and then creating amnesia for the memory that he was programmed and so we see\Nthe illness then is coming out of a program a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of course the hypnotic patient is this is happening as an experiment in a laboratory\Nbut let's forget let's not forget what happens in everyday life is that we've been hypnotized
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands and thousands of times we sit in a trance before the television set have no conscious\Nmemory the program went in and we are now subject to that for the rest of our life with no memory of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,where that came from because of childhood amnesia many people can't remember what happened before\Nthe age of five and so they're going to have a lot to deal with what's going on in my life right now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people even, you know, at a much later age, they have no memory of anything from their entire childhood or very few memories.\NEven people with good memories of their childhood, there are vast areas of vacant forgottenness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And in those areas of vacant forgottenness are the many programs which are now expressing later on in various forms of ill health.\NSuch catchphrases as heart disease runs in our family, overweight runs in our family, allergies run in our family, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has hay fever in our family.\NThese thoughts then become a program and it goes into the mind and we see that it's the same as though the person was hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that program is made conscious and cancelled, it remains operative within the unconscious.\NWe see another example of the power of mind over body in so-called cases of multiple personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These have been gaining increasing attention within the field of psychiatry\Nand it is found to be far more common.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was previously believed that the consciousness of one personality will be adopted and be operative within the person's body for varying periods of time.\NIt could be minutes, it could be hours, weeks, days, or even years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,While that personality is operative, while that second personality is operative,\Nthe person is subject to all the belief systems held by that personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So if that personality happens to believe I have an ulcer,\NI have a weight problem, I have allergies, I have diverticulitis, I have colitis, whatever it may believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have back trouble, so while that personality is operative within the body,\Nthose physical abnormalities actually are brought into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The reverse side of it is when that personality leaves and how that comes about is\Nsometimes intoxication or shifts of emotionality or life circumstances, suddenly the other personality comes into the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The other personality which has no such belief, the body promptly heals itself of all those illnesses.\NNow why does the mind have such power over the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can look at the physics of it a bit.\NThe physics would make it very easily understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We sit in our calibrated system here where death is zero and guilt is 30, 50, we went all the way up here.\NWe can get the energy field of anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we calibrate the energy field of the body,\Nthe physical body itself, and we find that the physical body is not a reversed state like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is not a negative state, but the energy field of the body is about 100.\NIn other words, its power, its energy field is about 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of mind begins here around 400.\NIt runs between 400 and 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the energy fields of the intellect, reason, logic, mind,\Nand beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore if we hold a thought in mind that says,\Nseeds like in a strawberry or caraway seeds or any kind of seeds give me diverticulitis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then the power of that thought, you see coming out of an energy field of between 400 and 500,\Nthe body which only has an energy field of 100 is overpowered by the power of the pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of that belief.\NAnd all thoughts have a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the form, which is there in the collective unconscious,\Nthe collective consciousness, the social consciousness, whatever you want to call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is there in great detail.\NThe pattern of that and the coming about of how the mechanics of that would happen is already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we buy into that thought, if we go into agreement with it,\Nit's like we bring it into our own unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that then expresses itself within the body.\NSo the body will do what the mind believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So the healing of the body then and the achievement of health\Nis achieved not by addressing the body directly but by addressing the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,moving right into the fields of consciousness itself.\NSo if the body is expressing that which is held in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then what we need to look at is what is being held in consciousness.\NVery often what's being held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we are not aware of.\NIn that case we call it being unconscious of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By looking at the body we may have no recall of ever having had such a thought.\NBut the body is telling us what must be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an x-ray.\NThe x-ray is telling us what must be held in mind for this to be presenting itself in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the person, let's say, develops clinical diabetes,\Nand he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything in my family.\NI don't remember anything in my family ever being said about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anybody in my family had diabetes.\NI don't see where it could have arisen in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that somewhere in the unconscious is the belief in diabetes\Nand all that goes with diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do individual research with the individual patient\Nlong enough and patiently enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we will uncover where the program came from.\NBut what it tells us is that the program is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That the person thinks, I am subject to that.\NAnd therefore the healing has to be of the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to heal where the origin of the illness starts.\NAnd so health comes out of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of positive mental attitudes.\NIt comes out of a field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of a level of consciousness\Nwhich expresses itself on the lower plane, the physical plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as an expression of health coming out of these fields above neutral.\NOut of willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the willingness to be accepting.\NOut of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of inner joyfulness.\NAnd out of an inner state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is mental was in the 400s.\NAnd that love is 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course spirit is 600 and above.\NActually spirit begins here once the needle moves to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes increasingly consciously aware that it is spirit.\NSo therefore the intellect is not man's highest faculty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Contrary to the age of reason and other learned works.\NOr those intellectuals who hold the thing that differentiates man from the animal is his intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is only in the 400s.\NThere is something beyond mind, beyond logic, beyond reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which jumps and transcends into a whole different paradigm,\Na whole different way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary to know about that.\NIt's necessary to know then that which heals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which is here on up.\NIt's necessary to look at the contribution that is coming into an illness from these various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that always with an illness,\Nif we now understand illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then we will understand its reverse,\Nwhich is health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That in illness there is always unconscious guilt.\NNever has there been an illness without unconscious guilt in our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an unconscious guilt and therefore the undoing of unconscious guilt.\NWe're not talking about conscious guilt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about unconscious guilt.\NAnd therefore there are whole systems of how to let go of unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,through the process of the willingness to forgive.\NMoving from here then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning the willingness to let go of judgment,\Nof criticism and judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to let go of make wrong,\Nof right wrong as an orientation towards life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and a willingness to move towards a forgivingness\Nand the desire to understand life out of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So moving out of the contribution of guilt\Nand all the negative emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we move up to the mind,\Nwe find that illness requires several things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires unconscious guilt\Nand it requires a mental belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind has to believe in a certain belief\Nfor the person to believe that they are subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though unconscious guilt\Nlooks for something to justify itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can be any illness out there\Nand we see that after a certain illness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gets popularized on television,\Nlet's say some celebrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,shares with us that particular illness\Nand that's followed by an epidemic of that illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of suggestion.\NThe mind now buys that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind buys the belief system\Nin the specificity of a particular disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt gives us\Nand gives it the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the unconscious guilt\Nlooking for an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through the autonomic nervous system\Nand through the hormonal system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and through all the stress mechanisms within the body\Nand through the acupuncture energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings us to the subject of kinesiology\Nwhich we mentioned in one of our other talks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of checking out for yourself\Nthese calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you who are familiar with kinesiology\Nknow how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who aren't,\NI can just briefly explain it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:22:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in about less than a minute.\NWhat you do is you press down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have somebody hold out their arm.\NYou look away from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you press down and ask them to resist.\NNow you ask them to hold something negative in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about in their life\Nover which they have grief or fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody they hate, let's say.\NAnd as you press,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,now you ask them to resist\Nand you press down again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see instantly the whole body goes weak.\NThe body goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,figuratively and symbolically\Nit goes weak on many levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if we ask the same person\Nto forget that and instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold in mind something or someone they love\Nand we press down again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll find that with all our strength\Nwe can't push their arm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are amazingly strong.\NThe brain hemispheres are synchronized,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the acupuncture energy system is balanced\Nand the energy flow of health,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of life is flowing correctly\Ndown all the energy channels
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and energizing all the organs of the body.\NSo that we see every time we hold a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then the energy flow down one of the 12 main meridians\Nis interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we habitually blow certain acupuncture meridians\Nthen disease comes about in that organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see that any of these negative emotions\Nis the direct cause of a disease process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt gives it enormous power\Nand the form that that illness takes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then is coming from mind,\Nwhat the mind believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the mind believes is what the body expresses.\NWe have to look at how experience is experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the body in and of itself\Nas we have said in other of these talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the body in and of itself is in ascension,\Nas curious as that may sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no capacity to experience itself.\NThe experience, the next level of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming through sensations\Ncoming from the senses of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:24:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't experience the body,\Nwe experience the senses of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Senses themselves have no capacity\Nto experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're experienced in mind.\NIt's because of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in mind that we experience the senses.\NAnd the senses then report what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,within the body.\NSo we're already several levels removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself isn't able to experience\Nits own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be in a greater, larger energy field\Nthan itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this case it is the energy field\Nof consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of consciousness\Nthat we're aware of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind then is telling us via the senses\Nwhat is going on in body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.13,0:24:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see that which we are,\Nwhen I say I, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.13,0:24:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is already several levels removed\Nfrom the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself requires\Nsomething greater than itself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we call awareness.\NAwareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is what allows us to know\Nwhat is going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.25,0:25:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,reporting what is happening within mind,\Nwhich in turn is reporting what is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,via the senses about the body.\NThat which is essentially myself then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is many levels removed from the physical body.\NIt's necessary for us to look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.85,0:25:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and get that correctly in mind\Nbecause now we see that it's the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.85,0:25:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that has power over the body.\NWe saw the physics of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.85,0:25:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy fields of the 400s\Njust by their sheer power
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.85,0:25:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are greater than that of the physical body.\NThe physical body does
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.85,0:25:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind tells it to do\Nand therefore if the mind says
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.85,0:25:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this disease or that disease\Nthe body complies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.85,0:25:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at this we see the importance then\Nof not buying into
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,programs\Nand all of which are really
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.85,0:25:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,limitations of the truth.\NWe see the importance of consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.95,0:26:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,cancelling and saying\Nsomething which is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is\NI am an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.87,0:26:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not subject to that.\NSo when we hear something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.00,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,like eggs which are\Nfull of cholesterol and their
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.00,0:26:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,cholesterol will give you heart disease.\NIf you buy into the thought form,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.44,0:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if you buy into that belief system\Nthat eggs, cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.44,0:26:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,will give me heart disease\Nraise my blood cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is that the body\Nagrees and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you eat cholesterol\Nwhat happens is your blood cholesterol goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experiment with this\Nbecause I've done it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.21,0:26:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and at one time I had a very high cholesterol\Nand I began to cancel the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept saying I'm an infinite being\NI'm not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.40,0:26:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.\NThis does not apply to me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:27:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hereby cancel it and refuse it.\NWell if the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.60,0:27:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can empower you with a\Nnegative belief system it can reverse itself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.60,0:27:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can it not?\NAnd therefore you begin telling yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.60,0:27:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have no effect on me\Nthat that's only a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.60,0:27:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't have to buy into that\NI don't have to go into agreement with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.66,0:27:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go into agreement with it\NI give it the power of the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.66,0:27:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of that belief.\NWhen I refuse it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,then I release myself from the collective\Nenergy of that belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.66,0:27:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I count myself out.\NSo one attitude then
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.85,0:27:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is to not buy into\Nagreement
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.85,0:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,with negative belief systems\Nhaving to do with your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very important\Nwhen it comes to epidemics
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.85,0:27:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the hysteria.\NSo you see the programming that comes in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is aided and abetted by\Nan emotional program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we hear much about AIDS\Nlet's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we hear about\Nconstant repetition in the media
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.04,0:28:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who play upon what?\NFear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.04,0:28:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear about this.\NAnger about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.04,0:28:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course guilt about this.\NWhat better disease to bring up all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.04,0:28:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,man's feelings of sinfulness\Nand guilt especially about his sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.04,0:28:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which is so common in our culture\Nin all cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the highest expression\Nof love of course
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.68,0:28:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when it takes on a negative\Nand when it is turned over
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.68,0:28:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the lowest.\NAnd therefore what a better area
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in which to create an epidemic\Nthrough sheer belief in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.68,0:28:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconscious guilt\Nnot to mention the conscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.68,0:28:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,about one's sexuality.\NThe sadness about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.68,0:28:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The grief over that.\NThe fear about the disease etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.68,0:28:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this contributing then\Nand setting the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.68,0:28:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have the mental belief system\Ncoming out of an energy field in the 400's.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:29:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have fear about it\Ncoming out of a negative 100's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.68,0:29:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have the guilt coming out\Nof the minus 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.68,0:29:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you have the exact set up for that.\NThe exact set up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.68,0:29:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind will choose\Nthat which
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.68,0:29:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is impressed with.\NAnd will use that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.68,0:29:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as a form of expression.\NIn the case of the cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiment I did with that\Nwith my own self
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,was to cancel the thought\Nthat came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.13,0:29:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And as time went by\Nin fact it didn't take very long
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.13,0:29:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with that particular thing\Nthe cholesterol level came down
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.13,0:29:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I can eat 3 eggs for breakfast\Nevery single morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of cheese.\NIn fact I live on a high cholesterol diet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.13,0:29:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet my cholesterol is low\Nand sometimes even below normal
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.12,0:29:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for my age.\NThe body will do exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.12,0:30:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind believes\Nand that's my belief in that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,make it happen within my life.\NIt's because of the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.70,0:30:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unconscious.\NIt creates the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.89,0:30:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for that to happen.\NWe certainly see that in accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.89,0:30:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is so called accident prone\Nthat's the form that is taken
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.89,0:30:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in that person's mind.\NUnconsciously they just manage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.89,0:30:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to get their body in the right place\Nat the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.89,0:30:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to get hit by the fender of the car\Nslip down the stairs, get hit on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.08,0:30:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will find a way.\NPeople will just slip into
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a hypnotic trance\Nand expose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.31,0:30:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the correct opportunities\Nto make that manifest within their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.44,0:30:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance with the cold virus\Nthere's many experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.44,0:30:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where we take 100 subject volunteers\Nand expose them to a very heavy dose
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of cold virus.\NWe see what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is that not everybody gets the cold virus.\NOnly a certain percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.44,0:31:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will always get it.\NIn other words if the power
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.50,0:31:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was in the virus rather than\Nwithin consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.50,0:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all 100 would get it\Nbecause that virus would be so potent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.50,0:31:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually what happens is\Nmaybe only 65%
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will get it.\NA third don't believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's sufficient doubt within the mind.\NThere's insufficient unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not acceptable to the person\Nto express it in that form.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is universal.\NWe see the same thing with healings.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.50,0:31:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Penicillin doesn't cure 100%\Nof pneumonias.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.50,0:31:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It only cures a certain percent.\NEvery medical treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.50,0:31:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has only a certain percentage\Nof people who will respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the difference?\NIt is because the others
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have sufficient unconscious guilt.\NIt's not operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.50,0:31:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular illness doesn't fit\Nany particular thought form
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.50,0:31:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have bought into.\NAnd so both sides of it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:32:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same.\NThe energy that we put into
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain belief system.\NSo we see then that health
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to let go\Nof buying into negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.98,0:32:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should a person buy into negativity anyway?\NWhy is it that some people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.98,0:32:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are so programmable?\NWe know people that go into hysteria
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,every time they open a magazine.\NThe latest illness sends them into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to do then\Nwith the amount of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.98,0:32:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the amount of guilt.\NIt's as though the person
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.98,0:32:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,knows what to be afraid of.\NIt's as though they're only too aware
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.98,0:32:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that because they have so much of this\Nfor them to even hear about it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.98,0:32:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and become mentally programmed\Nis almost enough to make it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.98,0:32:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in their life.\NSo what does this tell us then
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.08,0:32:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about the steps towards optimal health?\NIt means the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.08,0:32:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to adopt mental attitudes\Nthat are positive and constructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.08,0:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And this means the willingness\Nto let go of the negative ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:33:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to take an easy going\Nforgiving attitude towards life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.08,0:33:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The unwillingness\Nto buy into negative programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The owning\Nof the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.08,0:33:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, going into denial\Ngoing into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.46,0:33:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and blaming it\Non out there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is giving your power away.\NWe see that these energy fields below courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.52,0:33:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,here are all levels in which the person\Nhas become victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened is they've given\Ntheir power away
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.52,0:33:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it on something outside of themselves.\NAnd these people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.52,0:33:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in these levels here have said\Nto themselves unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.52,0:33:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of my happiness\Nis outside of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.52,0:33:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've put their survival on something\Noutside of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.52,0:33:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move into levels of truth\Nabove the levels of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy fields are now going positive\Nwe see that the person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.52,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is reowning their power.\NThe person is saying, I and I alone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,have the power to create\Nhappiness and opportunity in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is coming from within me.\NAnd so these people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.52,0:34:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then own that health\Nis something that comes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from within.\NThese people are coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.52,0:34:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the victim of disease.\NYou see, we are not the victim of viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.52,0:34:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of accidents.\NWe're not the victim of cholesterol.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.52,0:34:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the victim of uric acid levels.\NWe're not the victim of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.52,0:34:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reown our own power\Nwe say, hey, it's my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.62,0:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been creating that.\NMy mind believes that eating liver
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and kidneys is going to give you\Na high uric acid level
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's going to give you an attack of gout.\NMy mind is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.04,0:34:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I believe that\Nit will literally make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard thing for many people to accept\Nthat their mind has that much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.36,0:34:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me that if I believe\Nthat eating sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.36,0:34:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to give me hypoglycemia\Nthat that will give me hypoglycemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.36,0:35:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed it will.\NAnd so we go back to the physics involved
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.36,0:35:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and we remind ourselves\Nthat the body's energy field of 100
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.36,0:35:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is weak compared to the belief systems of 400.\NThe belief that sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.36,0:35:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,will give me hypoglycemia\Nor give me diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.36,0:35:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or give me overweight.\NThose belief systems are sufficient to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.68,0:35:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the explanations\Nthat we come upon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.68,0:35:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the rationalizations\Nthat justify that we are the victim of that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are just that.\NThey're not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.68,0:35:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're substituting an explanation.\NThe fact that it's scientific
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.12,0:35:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is still an explanation.\NThe science of it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.12,0:35:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the mechanism.\NThe description of the mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of how this comes about on the physical plane\Nis only a description
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.12,0:35:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mechanism.\NIt is not a description of cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.12,0:35:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is on the level of mind.\NEffect is on the level of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:36:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the other way around.\NAnd if we really just merely reverse
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that understanding,\Nwe have the whole key to health and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.12,0:36:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Health then comes out of a positive\Nmental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.12,0:36:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a thing we've heard many times, haven't we?\NIn fact, many people are annoyed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.12,0:36:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because that infers if I have a sickness\NI don't have a positive mental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.12,0:36:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at mental attitude then.\NLet's look at what is meant by that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.22,0:36:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the part that that plays in\Nhealth and freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.22,0:36:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from sickness and suffering.\NWe said the one thing that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.28,0:36:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in the unhealthy person is\Nthis unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.28,0:36:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cure for that\Nis the willingness to be forgiving,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to actually take courses in forgiveness\Nif that is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the Course in Miracles,\Nwhich is specifically designed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.28,0:36:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of that tendency of the mind\Nto criticize, to attack, and to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.35,0:36:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then\Nto let go judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the mechanism is unconscious,\Nso the person may not see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.38,0:37:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the connection between\Nthe fact that their mind is critical
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgmental.\NIf your mind is critical and judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.38,0:37:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of others, of course it is critical\Nand judgmental of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.38,0:37:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The creation of the unconscious guilt\Nthen builds up a certain energy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.38,0:37:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which expresses itself through\Nthe autonomic nervous system
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.38,0:37:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the acupuncture energy system.\NSo that is the cure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.38,0:37:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The contribution from mind,\Nthe belief system,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.38,0:37:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we said is the power of refusal,\Nto deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.83,0:37:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your power now\Nthat it is the mind and the mind itself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the cause of the illness.\NThe willingness to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.83,0:37:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the position of victim,\Nthe willingness to reown one's own power
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.83,0:37:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is part and parcel of the third thing\Nthat is necessary for health,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.83,0:37:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is one's overall\Nspiritual growth and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.83,0:37:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The overall moving out of\Nthese negative energy patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.83,0:37:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to face truths\Nwithin ourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.83,0:38:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moving into a positive energy field.\NThis can be done actually rather rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.37,0:38:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?\NBecause willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.37,0:38:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, is the key.\NThrough the willingness to look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.37,0:38:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to say,\Nwell, I don't really believe this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.37,0:38:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is said that my mind has the power\Nto create an illness within my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.37,0:38:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I am willing to look at that\Nbecause I have an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.37,0:38:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an open mind\Nand I am willing to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.37,0:38:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My intention aligns then\Nand I begin to move into accepting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.47,0:38:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which I discover.\NI begin to find
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.47,0:38:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that moving into lovingness\Nhas a curative and healing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.47,0:38:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do we do that?\NOur willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.47,0:38:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,our willingness here moves us\Nright into the willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.47,0:38:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we\Ncan quickly move ourself into
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to be compassionate.\NWhat does compassion mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.17,0:38:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion means\Nthe willingness to see the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.40,0:39:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within all things.\NYou see, that coincides
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the willingness to forgive.\NOut of compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.40,0:39:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,comes the power,\Nthe capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of our intention\Nto really see into the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.40,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When we see into the hearts of others,\Nas we've said in other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what we discover is the innocence\Nof the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.40,0:39:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within each and every one of us\Nbecause it is intrinsic to the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself,\Nis that intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.43,0:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which never dies\Nno matter how long we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.43,0:39:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence of the child\Nis what bought the mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.43,0:39:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which bought the negative program\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.43,0:39:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The being aware,\Nthat that intrinsic innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.43,0:39:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is ever with us.\NIt's the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.43,0:39:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that sits there in front of the television set\Nand buys the negative programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.00,0:39:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of its naivete,\Nout of its lack of discernment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.00,0:40:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the child\Nsays,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.00,0:40:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a world\Nthat is out to program you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.00,0:40:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with as much negativity\Nas you're willing to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.20,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it gets well paid to do that\Nbecause advertising is usually based
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in playing off of these negative energy fields.\NAll of our fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.20,0:40:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our desires,\Nall of our pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it as you see below the line.\NThe willingness then
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.20,0:40:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware\Nthat within us is our innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.20,0:40:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the innocence\Nneeds to be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.20,0:40:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we come into what's called self-care.\NSelf-care,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to love oneself now,\Nmeans taking responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.20,0:40:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect ourselves\Nfrom that innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.20,0:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the willingness\Nto undo the mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.20,0:40:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the mind picked up\Nas a result of its innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle now\Nlooking at ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.23,0:41:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing that which we find within us\Nif we're coming from the compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.23,0:41:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the awareness\Nof the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.23,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our consciousness.\NWe see that it was innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.26,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that got programmed.\NNow we take responsibility for that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we say, well,\Nin my innocence I bought all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In my innocence I didn't know any better.\NIn my innocence I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that the right thing to do\Nwas to be judgmental,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to condemn people,\Nto judge them as right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to let it go.\NWe have amongst our acquaintances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.80,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people that we've done research\Nwith people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.28,0:41:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who have had every disease known to mankind,\Nadvanced multiple sclerosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cancers of all kinds,\Nall kinds of advanced illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.28,0:41:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And these people\Nmerely were willing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.28,0:41:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to look into this question.\NAnd when they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:42:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they went through the processes\Nthat we've described in this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.28,0:42:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all came out\Nof their illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.28,0:42:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,without any residuals whatsoever.\NThis capacity then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.24,0:42:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to be forgiving is within us,\Nthe capacity for compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.24,0:42:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of it comes\Na general attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a way in which we look at ourself.\NSo from our bigness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.24,0:42:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from our greatness,\Nwe look at our humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,through forgiving eyes\Nand we begin to forgive ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.24,0:42:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the things\Nthat were limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.24,0:42:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth.\NAll of these things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.24,0:42:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with an energy fuel\Nwith the arrows going to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.24,0:42:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are denials of the truth.\NAll of those with an arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.24,0:42:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the right\Nis the acceptance of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.72,0:42:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which is true and positive.\NAnd so health,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.72,0:42:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because the body is reflecting\Nwhat the mind believes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:43:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind is reflecting\Nour spiritual position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.72,0:43:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit has the greatest power of all.\NIt is willing to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.72,0:43:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of mind.\NNow we have to be attentive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.72,0:43:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have to persevere\Nand we can't let it get away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.72,0:43:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with expressing negativity\Nwithout stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we get to develop\Nsort of an ear for negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.72,0:43:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to recognize it\Nfor what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.84,0:43:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go of false humility\Nand we start questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.91,0:43:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,such remarks as,\Noh, my handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.91,0:43:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or I gain weight\Nin the same amount of food
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.91,0:43:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that other people stay thin.\NThe minute we hear ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.91,0:43:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,saying these limiting,\Nself-defeating, self-attacking thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.91,0:43:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to be stopped and canceled.\NThe handwriting is poor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.91,0:43:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's a belief system\Nthat I have poor handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.07,0:43:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and not vice versa.\NSo what we're doing then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.07,0:44:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is reversing the whole programming\Nof the mind as far as
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.10,0:44:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we're coming back to a principle\Nwhich you can demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.10,0:44:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own experience.\NThat the physical is the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.32,0:44:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mental and not vice versa.\NIt isn't that we came to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.32,0:44:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,our handwriting is poor\Nbecause our handwriting is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.32,0:44:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting is poor\Nbecause the cause was in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.32,0:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The belief system.\NPerhaps a remark
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,picked up in childhood.\NSomebody says your handwriting is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.32,0:44:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From that point on that program\Nwe have to look at the ingenuity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.87,0:44:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unconscious mind.\NTo really see it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.06,0:44:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be great if you had\Nsome experience in watching
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.06,0:44:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,hypnotic experiments.\NBecause if we tell the person
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.06,0:44:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that when they wake up\Ntheir legs will be itching
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we induce amnesia\Nfor that suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.06,0:45:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When we wake the person up\Nwe'll say how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.06,0:45:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly the mind will start\Ncreating the most marvelous
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.06,0:45:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,things.\NThe person doesn't just say
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.06,0:45:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well my legs itch.\NThe mind always gets in there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.06,0:45:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in a creative way\Nand will say and start explaining
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.06,0:45:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well I've got wool pants on\Nand you know I'm allergic to wool
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the heat in this room\Nand steam heat always creates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.06,0:45:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just marvelous to listen\Nto the inventiveness of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.06,0:45:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as it begins to create\Nthe reasons for the symptom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.06,0:45:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will do the same thing then\Nand it's helpful to look at ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.44,0:45:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as though we've been hypnotized\Nsubjects half of our life
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.44,0:45:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't even realize it.\NWhat is hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.44,0:45:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suggestibility is it not?\NIt means to be in an unguarded
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.44,0:45:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestible relaxed state.\NSo anytime you've been
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.44,0:45:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in an unguarded relaxed\Nsuggestible state
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.44,0:46:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you've picked up all the programming\Nand whether you remember it or not
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.44,0:46:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it is still operative.\NHalf asleep as you sat in front
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.44,0:46:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the television set\Nhour after hour after hour
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.44,0:46:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of programming went into the mind.\NThese are all now
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.44,0:46:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious\Nhypnotic programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.48,0:46:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we discover what we've been programmed?\NWith is by watching
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.48,0:46:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what comes up.\NSo the idea oh I'm no good
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.48,0:46:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no good.\NI never was very good at playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.15,0:46:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the belief system\Nthat you're not very good at playing cards
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to operate in your life\Nis that you're not going to be very good
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.15,0:46:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at playing cards.\NThat goes back then to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.15,0:46:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the belief system.\NAnd so these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.15,0:46:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,become self reinforcing.\NThey become self fulfilling prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.15,0:46:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold the belief unwittingly\Nit then manifests in our life
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.15,0:46:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we look at that and we say see\Nand that justifies the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.47,0:47:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So by looking at our life\Nwe can tell what beliefs we are holding
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.47,0:47:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if we can't recall them\Ntherefore our movement
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.47,0:47:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is upward in consciousness\Nwe said health is the automatic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.47,0:47:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of these energy fields up here.\NThe energy field of 540 and over
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.47,0:47:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which is one of gratitude\Nand forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.47,0:47:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that gratitude is at 540\Nforgiveness is at 540
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.47,0:47:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing\Nis at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.47,0:47:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to be forgiving\Nand grateful in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.47,0:47:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically begins to heal.\NBecoming a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.46,0:47:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,loving being.\NThis energy field of love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.46,0:47:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we must talk about what that means.\NIt doesn't talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.46,0:47:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not sentimentality.\NWhat the world calls love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.46,0:47:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out in an energy field\Nin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's talking about dependency\Nit's talking about control
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.46,0:47:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's talking about sentimentalism\Nand emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.46,0:48:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotional sentimental attachment\Nin which there is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.46,0:48:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,control going back and forth\Nand the satisfaction of desiringness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.46,0:48:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on both sides\Nis called love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.46,0:48:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hollywood version.\NWhen you hear somebody say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to love George but I don't anymore\Nwhat it means is that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.75,0:48:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they never did love George.\NWhat it means is they had a sentimental attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.75,0:48:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a solar plexus\Nkind of a hanging onto
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.75,0:48:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which the person then\Nromanticized and glamorized
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,within their life\Nand poured a lot of emotional energy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.75,0:48:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,into their life\Nand when that was broken
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.88,0:48:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,up came a lot of negative emotion.\NThe kind of love we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is unconditional love.\NUnconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.97,0:48:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is unconditional love?\NThat's an inner decision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.97,0:48:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that we make within ourself.\NSee the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.97,0:48:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out of the intention\Nand the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.97,0:49:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a loving person.\NSo if I decide to love you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.97,0:49:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that is my inner decision.\NTherefore I'm not the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.97,0:49:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of what goes on in the world\Nbecause my decision to love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.97,0:49:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a stable energy field\Nof unconditionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.97,0:49:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other person's behavior\Nmay not please me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.97,0:49:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,may not contribute\Nto what I desire
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.26,0:49:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't change the lovingness.\NSo the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.26,0:49:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance who visits her son in prison\Nfor 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.26,0:49:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the son who is a murderer\Nloves the beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.26,0:49:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the is-ness\Nthat which the person really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.26,0:49:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course his behavior\Ndoes not make her happy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.26,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but the love is unconditional\Nno matter what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.26,0:49:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the closest to it\Nthat we see in our world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.26,0:49:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the lovingness of the mother\Nwhich is unconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.26,0:49:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The lovingness of 12 step groups\Nsuch as Alcoholics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.26,0:50:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've used as an example\Nin other talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.74,0:50:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconditionality of that lovingness.\NIt's not concerned with what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.74,0:50:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not concerned with what you have.\NThe people at the bottom here
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.74,0:50:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,are very concerned with havingness\Nand rate people back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.74,0:50:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on what they have.\NIn the middle of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,people are preoccupied with doingness\Nand people are rated
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.74,0:50:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and their status depends on what you do\Nand all the titles that go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.74,0:50:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with your doingness.\NAs you move towards the top of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.74,0:50:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what people are concerned with\Nis what you are, what you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.74,0:50:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are beingness\Nthat which you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.03,0:50:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're concerned there\Nwith a person's status
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.03,0:50:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,their value there\Nis the kind of a person that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.03,0:50:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become\Nyou have become that kind of a person
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.03,0:50:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what is valued.\NThe willingness then to become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.03,0:51:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a forgiving person\Nwho nurtures all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.06,0:51:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,non-judgmentally\Nautomatically brings about within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.06,0:51:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the very healing nature\Na condition of good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning to see\Nthe perfection of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.09,0:51:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,how all things work out for the good.\NHow can illness be
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.09,0:51:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,held in that context?\NFor the person who is oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.60,0:51:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,such in the direction in which\Nwe're talking today
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.60,0:51:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then illness merely becomes\Nsomething that is coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.64,0:51:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to be healed.\NWe look at the illness then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.64,0:51:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as bringing up a lesson.\NThe illness is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.64,0:51:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,please heal what I stand for\Nwhat I symbolize.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.64,0:51:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal your guiltiness.\NPlease heal your self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.92,0:51:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please heal your limiting thought forms.\NPlease move up to loving me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.92,0:51:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can be healed.\NAnd so the illness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.92,0:51:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is a demand\Nto grow spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.92,0:52:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an incessant\Ngadfly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.92,0:52:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that tells us\Nthat something is out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.92,0:52:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,something needs to be looked at\Nto be held in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.92,0:52:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see because it is not\Nthe events of life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.92,0:52:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but how we hold them\Nthat creates our reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.92,0:52:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Events in and of themselves\Nhave no power
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.92,0:52:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to affect how we feel\None way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.92,0:52:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what our position is about them.\NIt's our judgment about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.92,0:52:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how we decide to be with them.\NIt's our attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.92,0:52:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our point of view.\NIt's the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.92,0:52:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see\Nwe are the creator then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.50,0:52:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the meaning\Nthe impact that it has on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.50,0:52:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress comes from\Nthat very thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.50,0:52:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving it power over our lives\Ncoming from the position of victim
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.50,0:52:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,putting the source of happiness\Noutside of our life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.50,0:53:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,denying the power of our own mind.\NThe healing then comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,through the re-owning of the power\Nthe realization that we and we alone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.50,0:53:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,create\Nthe meaning of any
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.50,0:53:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,circumstance, event,\Nplace, position or thing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.50,0:53:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,any person in our life.\NWe are the one that creates the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our position, the way we hold it then\Nthat either becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.88,0:53:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a source of healing\Nor a source of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.88,0:53:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the one that determines that.\NIt's her little pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.88,0:53:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words\Nwe begin to see that the body
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.88,0:53:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a little marionette.\NYou know it sort of happily goes about its way
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.88,0:53:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,energy fuels of joyfulness and gladness.\NYou see it just sort of does
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.88,0:53:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what it does automatically\Nwithout much thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.88,0:53:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthy means we pay less and less\Nattention to the body
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.88,0:53:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which we do\Nwhich the world would call health giving
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.88,0:53:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of appreciation\Nit's an expression of how we are
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.88,0:54:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with that body.\NYou see we aren't giving away
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.88,0:54:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,our power as source.\NBeing healthy means you've re-owned
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.88,0:54:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your power as source.\NYou're not giving away the source
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.88,0:54:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of health of the body to the world.\NThe exercising we do
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.27,0:54:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of the joyfulness\Nin experiencing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.27,0:54:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't say that swimming\Nis what causes the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.27,0:54:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to be healthy.\NWe come from the position
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.27,0:54:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that because we enjoy the body\Nwe enjoy its activity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.27,0:54:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,such as swimming.\NSo those activities which the world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.65,0:54:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,consider healthy\Nthen are coming out of the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.65,0:54:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's inner sense of aliveness.\NThe joy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.65,0:54:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in allowing the body's\Nexpression in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.65,0:54:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world considers healthy.\NNot because they're causal
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.65,0:54:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the effect.\NThe healthy enjoyment of the body then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.65,0:54:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is the effect of the mental attitude.\NLooking at it as something pleasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.65,0:55:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we come to a\Nlovingness of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.65,0:55:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not a narcissistic\Nself-glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.65,0:55:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a muscle man\Na picture in the photo magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.65,0:55:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not out of desiringness\Nnot out of pridefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.65,0:55:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of narcissism\Nbut out of a lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.65,0:55:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and a gratitude.\NWe say ah little body
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.65,0:55:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you've served me well\NI love you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.65,0:55:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you\NI value you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.65,0:55:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See we know we are not the body.\NIf you lose your right arm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.81,0:55:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll still say I am me.\NIf you lose your left arm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.81,0:55:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if you lose both legs\Nyou'll still be saying I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.81,0:55:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take off the ears\Nprogressively the body diminishes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.81,0:55:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to practically nothing\Nand yet the sense of self
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.81,0:55:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is ever with us.\NAnd so the healthy person
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.97,0:55:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to develop a sense of self\Nthat is independent of external events
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.97,0:56:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and independent\Nof being the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.97,0:56:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is aware\Nthat the body is the body
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.97,0:56:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of events but I am me.\NAnd that which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.97,0:56:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is really untouched by these events.\NThe self that wakes up every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.97,0:56:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even begins to remember\Nyou know name and address
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.97,0:56:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you are\Nand what you're supposed to do today
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.97,0:56:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that self remains unimpaired.\NThe innocence of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.97,0:56:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the hardware of the computer\Nis unaffected by the software
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.97,0:56:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the events that go through life.\NAnd so a healthy attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.97,0:56:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is one which does not put\Nthe person in transitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.00,0:56:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look back at this chart\Nwe'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.26,0:56:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened here\Nis that the person has placed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.26,0:56:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,their survival on something\Noutside of themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.26,0:56:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This something outside of oneself\Nis always transitory
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.26,0:56:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and changing in nature.\NWe can say the one thing we know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.26,0:57:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world for certain\Nis that all things change.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.26,0:57:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All things change.\NConsequently if we put the source
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.26,0:57:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our survival on that\Nwhich is outside of ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.26,0:57:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,our job, our possessions\Na particular relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.26,0:57:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then we're merely setting ourself up\Nfor the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.26,0:57:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our health\Nbecause what's going to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.26,0:57:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all is fear of loss\Neven though that's not conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.26,0:57:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know if the source of your happiness\Nis your title and your position
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and your address and the kind of car\Nthat you have etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.26,0:57:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or even the beauty of the physical body\Nthat you have
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.26,0:57:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're vulnerable.\NSo that vulnerability
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.26,0:57:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the unconscious\Nand it stores up a great deal of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.26,0:57:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore people's lives become\Nendlessly to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.26,0:57:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and protect themselves from the loss\Nof those things upon which
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.90,0:57:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they have put their survival.\NThe healthy person realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.90,0:58:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the true nature of who they really are.\NThat they are something far beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.90,0:58:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That they are the one\Nthat gives those things value.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.90,0:58:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That they are temporary enjoyment\Nbut their survival doesn't depend on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.90,0:58:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that when you move up\Ninto this energy fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.28,0:58:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,called acceptance\None has stopped giving one's power
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.28,0:58:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,away to the world.\NOne has begun to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.28,0:58:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am the source of my happiness.\NThat if you put a person like that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.28,0:58:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on a desert island and come back a year later\Nyou know they'll have a coconut business going
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.28,0:58:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll have found a new relationship\Nand they'll build a tree house in the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.28,0:58:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll be teaching the children algebra.\NThat they have the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.28,0:58:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to recreate for themselves\Nthe source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.28,0:58:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from the realization\Nthat I myself am the source of that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.28,0:58:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself am the source of health.\NIt doesn't depend on epidemics.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.28,0:58:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on what is out there in the world.\NIt doesn't depend on what I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.41,0:59:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When we really realize that\Nthen we begin to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.41,0:59:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and no longer be at the effect\Nof all these false belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.41,0:59:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what kind of a life\Nis possible then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.41,0:59:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from canceling these belief systems.\NThe mind says,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.41,0:59:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uh-oh, you cancel these belief systems\Nand you're really going to be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.48,0:59:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see here is a mind that has placed its security\Nit's based its security
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.48,0:59:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on the worshipping of fear.\NThe worshipping of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.51,0:59:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is saying, by paying attention\Nto these fearful thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.51,0:59:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and complying with them\Nthat's why
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.51,0:59:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am alive.\NA mind like that says
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.51,0:59:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason my house hasn't been robbed\Nis because I lock all my doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.51,0:59:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't see\Nthat it's the power of the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.83,0:59:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind thinks\Nif the doors are locked
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.83,0:59:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the house won't be robbed.\NIt's the power of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.83,0:59:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that's keeping the house from being robbed.\NIt isn't the locking of the doors at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.37,1:00:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As anybody knows\Nan accomplished thief will go through any lock.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.37,1:00:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no lock made that will hold back an accomplished thief.\NThey'll go through the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.37,1:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your doors locked.\NZip, zip, zip, they're in through the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.44,1:00:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip, zip, zip, they're through the ceiling.\NThey're through the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.44,1:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're through the wall.\NSomebody wants in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.44,1:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not kid ourselves.\NThey're going to get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.44,1:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an amateur like myself.\NGive me 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.44,1:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and a trunk load of tools\Nand I'm going to be in that house.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.85,1:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the thought.\NThe power of the belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.85,1:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the lock.\NIt's the power of the belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.85,1:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to undo its mistakes.\NThe willingness to be
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.85,1:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiving and compassionate.\NThe realization through wisdom
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.24,1:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that I make myself victim\Nwhen I place the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.24,1:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,outside myself.\NAnd so what happens is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.24,1:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to recontextualize our life.\NWe begin to say
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.24,1:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that gives my life meaning?\NWhat is it that I really value?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.24,1:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that if you removed\Nfrom my life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.24,1:01:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if you took away my job\Nand you took away my position
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.24,1:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what meaning would my life have then?\NWhat would it be worth?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.24,1:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I willing to die for?\NAnd so some introspection
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.24,1:01:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual movement is necessary\Nto achieve a state of well-being.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.24,1:01:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that one's life\Nis significant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.24,1:01:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That we make a difference in the world.\NWe don't need the attention
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.81,1:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that illness brings to us\Nbecause our sense of importance
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.81,1:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,comes about through the realization\Nand willingness of our real self.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.81,1:01:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And so general growth\Nin the whole field
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.81,1:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual development\Nbrings about a condition of health.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.81,1:01:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can do so quite rapidly.\NTo change your position
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.81,1:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go a certain limiting belief\Ndoesn't take very long at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.81,1:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the realization\Nthat you have the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.81,1:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And secondly\Nis the willingness to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.81,1:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To verify through your own experience.\NIt isn't necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.81,1:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the words of others.\NThe words of others are only an inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.81,1:02:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have enough faith in them\Nto say, well, it sounds so
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.81,1:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to give it a try.\NAnd therefore in my own particular
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.81,1:02:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,personal experience\Nas well as clinical experience
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.91,1:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen illnesses go in a matter of\Nminutes, days, weeks, months
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.91,1:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the most a chronic illness\Nthat lasted for 25 years
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.91,1:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps took two years\Nbut it was constantly doing the processes
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.20,1:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've described today.\NThe willingness to accept the power of mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.20,1:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to never allow the mind\Nto say something negative
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.20,1:02:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without challenging it\Nand replacing it with a positive thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.20,1:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go\Nbeing judgmental towards ourselves and others
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.20,1:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of the letting go of the negative.\NWhy is this so?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.48,1:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so because\Nthe energy field of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.48,1:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which gives us\Nan intense sense of aliveness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go of the obstacles to it\Nis ever present.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.48,1:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What we call bliss\Nis the vibration of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.48,1:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We could call all that is\Nat the top of this chart
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.48,1:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is God\Nthat which is spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.48,1:03:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is one's higher power\Nwhat Krishnamurti calls what is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.48,1:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,isness, beingness\Nthe energy of that is the energy of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.48,1:03:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly present, ever present.\NLike the sun
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.12,1:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it is always shining\Nbut because of these clouds here
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.12,1:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't experience it.\NIt is not necessary to program ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.12,1:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with the truth.\NIt is only necessary to remove
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.12,1:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is false.\NThe removal of the clouds from the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.12,1:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the elimination of the negative\Nallows one to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.12,1:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy fields\Nof that which is positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.12,1:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is only the removal of the negative\Nthat is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.12,1:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go\Nof habits of negative thinking, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.12,1:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal\Nof the obstacles
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.54,1:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,through the experiencing of this\Nwill result in an increasing sense
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.54,1:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of aliveness.\NWith it, a joy of one's own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.54,1:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As this joy\Nof one's own existence comes in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.54,1:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,first subtly and then stronger and stronger\Nthere is a diminished
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness even of the presence\Nof the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.67,1:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One's physicalness\Nas one gets up into higher levels of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.67,1:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a joyfulness\Nthe body is looked to as a source of pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.67,1:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it is held as a pleasure\Na pleasurable
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.73,1:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoyable experience.\NBut as we move towards
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.73,1:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of the box\Nthe experiencing of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.73,1:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to diminish altogether.\NThere is a progressive experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.73,1:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of joy which is diffuse.\NThere is an inner progressive
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.73,1:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,state of serenity accompanied by\Na peaceful blissfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.73,1:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this point\Nthe experience of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.73,1:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,may disappear altogether\Ninto sort of a sublime
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.73,1:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,state in which one is\Njoyful
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.73,1:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,aliveness.\NOne is that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.73,1:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,loving bliss.\NAt that point the awareness of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.73,1:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,may be almost nil.\NIt's as though it's present in the room
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.73,1:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's no more\Nimportant than anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.73,1:05:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in the room.\NThat loss of identification
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.76,1:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the body.\NAnd we watch the body from that viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.76,1:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,going about its business happily\Nbut we are no more concerned
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.76,1:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about it than we are\Nanything else in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.76,1:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That loss of identification\Nwith the separate limited self.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.76,1:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The loss of identification\Nwith the limited physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.76,1:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And with it of course the body\Nis expressing the absolute truth
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.76,1:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite truth\Nthat one is the infinite beingness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.76,1:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universe.\NAnd therefore the value
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.96,1:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of replacing a negative thought\Ninto the empty
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,space of that\Nin the place that we just cancel
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.96,1:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we place the statement\NI am an infinite being and I am not
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.96,1:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,subject to that.\NI am an infinite being and I am not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.96,1:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything that we cancel\Nwe replace with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.96,1:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In place of the negative thought\Nwe put something in that's positive
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.98,1:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because we choose to love\Nourself instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.98,1:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can also use the form we can say\NI cancel that. I no longer buy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.98,1:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to that.\NInstead I choose to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.98,1:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead I choose to love myself.\NAnd so we see that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.98,1:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness then\Nis the great healer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.98,1:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have within our capacity\Nwithin the power within us
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all the powers of self healing.\NAll we have to do is remove the obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.98,1:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect health\Nis an expression then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.98,1:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual awareness.\NThe willingness to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the negative\Nand allowing it to be replaced by that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.98,1:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is loving.\NSo the physical expression then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.04,1:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is of this energy field.\NSickness is merely an expression
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.04,1:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of this energy field\Ndown here
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.04,1:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,given form by what is held in mind.\NPhysical health
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.17,1:07:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is merely an expression\Nof a positive energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.17,1:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,reinforced by our\Nwillingness to commit
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.17,1:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to compassion and forgiveness.\NThat which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.17,1:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,includes the body\Nnot limited to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.24,1:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am chooses to love it\Nto value it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.88,1:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to be appreciative of it\Nto be grateful for it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.94,1:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to enjoy the sense of aliveness.\NWe get into
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.94,1:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of the experiencing\Nof experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.94,1:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We get more and more into the awareness\Nof the joy and the thankfulness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.94,1:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for our existence.\NThe existence of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.94,1:08:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of our consciousness.\NThe body is then included
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.94,1:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,within the field of consciousness itself.\NWe come to the surprising thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.94,1:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body\Nis within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.94,1:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people\Nhaving a limited belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.94,1:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will think that the mind\Nis somewhere up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.94,1:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually when you experience experience\Nif you try to localize it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.94,1:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that it is everywhere.\NWhen you experience a thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.94,1:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it is being experienced everywhere.\NThe thought that it is occurring
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.04,1:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in here\Nwithin your system
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.04,1:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a thought about thought.\NInner experience will tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.68,1:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that the experience of a thought\Nthe experience of the body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.68,1:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is occurring everywhere.\NIt is occurring in consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.68,1:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that the body\Nis sitting in the chair
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.68,1:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but where is that understanding\Nbeing experienced?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.68,1:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That understanding is being experienced\Nin no specific place.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is happening within\Nyour consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.87,1:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The health then is really\Naddressing ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.87,1:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to the nature of consciousness.\NThe body then is coming out
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.87,1:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of our sense of aliveness\Nwhich is coming out of our
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.87,1:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of appreciation\Nfor our own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.87,1:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In this talk we have repeated\Ncertain things over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.87,1:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the mind's resistance\Nto accepting the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.93,1:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain learning is really\None of becoming familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.93,1:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly re-exposing ourselves\Nuntil it becomes natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.93,1:09:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it difficult when it comes\Nto healing and health?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.93,1:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because we are really reversing\Nthe mind's belief in causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.93,1:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We are saying that the physical\Nis the expression of the mental
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.25,1:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and not vice versa.\NYou see the world would like to say
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.25,1:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it is the other way around\Nthat cause is within the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.25,1:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is within the powers\Nwithin the virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.25,1:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is within the bacteria.\NEven medications work because
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.25,1:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the belief in the power\Nof the medication.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.25,1:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly see this with scientific research\Ninto the nature of placebos.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.25,1:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Placebos alone will cure 35%\Ngenerally of people with any given ailment.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.25,1:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the suggestion\Nthat this pill will heal it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.25,1:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,35% of the time\Nis all that is sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.25,1:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizing then\Nthat we are making a major move
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.99,1:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness allows us\Nto value
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.99,1:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our knowledge about\Nconsciousness and health
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.99,1:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to use it as a springboard\Nto our own spiritual growth and development.
